actual = []
pp = OptimizingPostprocessor()
pp.callback = actual.append
pp.process(a1)
pp.process(a2)
pp.done()
for x, y in zip_longest(actual, [a1, a2]):
    assert repr(x) == repr(y)
pytest.mark.parametrize('a1, a2', [(Rotate(Side.LEFT, True), Rotate(Side.
    TOP, False)), (Rotate(Side.LEFT, True), Turn(Side.TOP, 1)), (Turn(
    TurningType.HORIZONTAL, [1], 1), Turn(TurningType.VERTICAL, [1], 1)), (
    Turn(TurningType.HORIZONTAL, [1], 1), Turn(TurningType.HORIZONTAL, [2],
    1))])
